/**
 * parent/pages/BookReaderPage.tsx
 * ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
 * ULTIMATE AI ANIMATED STORYBOOK READER
 *
 * Premium EdTech-level flipbook reader for Class 1 NCERT books.
 *
 * Features:
 *  ①  react-pageflip two-page spread (desktop) / single (mobile)
 *  ②  Realistic page turn with shadow, bending, fold effects
 *  ③  📖 Reading Mode | 🎬 Story Mode toggle
 *  ④  Page illustration animations (sun glow, clouds float, birds fly…)
 *  ⑤  🔊 Read Aloud — AI narration with word highlighting
 *  ⑥  Word tap → Explain / Pronounce / Example popup
 *  ⑦  🤖 Ask AI about this page — sliding chat panel
 *  ⑧  🎮 Mini activities — quiz, vocab, fun facts
 *  ⑨  Focus Reading mode — dims illustrations, highlights text
 *  ⑩  AI Learning Tracker — pages, time, words, quizzes
 *  ⑪  Page progress bar + page counter
 *  ⑫  Wooden table background + book depth shadow
 *  ⑬  Mobile single-page + flip animation
 *  ⑭  Lazy load ±2 pages around current
 *  ⑮  Pastel glass theme throughout
 */

